    v0 = (wp.cos(0.26) / 0.05)
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.82 / v0 + 0.49) * (tmp + 0.72 * v1 + 0.12)) / v0)
    v2 = (0.27 + wp.abs((tmp + 0.64 / tmp + 0.67)))
    tmp = wp.sin((v2 / wp.sin(v2 + 0.61)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.49)
